WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:02.266
May the Empress Dowager have long life and peace.

2
00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:04.466
Quickly pay your respects to the Emperor.

3
00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:11.066
I pay my respects to Your Majesty.

4
00:00:11.166 --> 00:00:12.666
I pay my respects to the Noble Consort.

5
00:00:14.200 --> 00:00:16.766
Mother, what is going on?

6
00:00:16.766 --> 00:00:20.566
Yesterday, the National Consort brought Wan Ning to visit me.

7
00:00:20.566 --> 00:00:23.000
I found this child very likable.

8
00:00:23.066 --> 00:00:24.800
So I made her a Noble Consort.

9
00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:27.900
The Emperor has no objections, right?

10
00:00:27.900 --> 00:00:28.966
I dare not object.

11
00:00:29.066 --> 00:00:30.433
But I think

12
00:00:30.566 --> 00:00:32.533
Mother should have consulted with me first.

13
00:00:32.533 --> 00:00:34.800
I did not act impulsively like the Emperor did.

14
00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:37.300
I did not act rashly like Xia Zhi Feng did.

15
00:00:37.866 --> 00:00:39.300
Where is Noble Consort Long?

16
00:00:41.333 --> 00:00:43.166
I am very satisfied.

17
00:00:43.366 --> 00:00:45.466
It seems the Empress Dowager treats me like a second Yan Guifei.

18
00:00:45.466 --> 00:00:48.566
Otherwise, why would there be such trouble?

19
00:00:48.566 --> 00:00:50.400
Making her niece deal with me.

20
00:00:51.933 --> 00:00:54.200
Then we will take our leave now.

21
00:00:54.266 --> 00:00:56.500
We won’t disturb the Empress Dowager and her niece any longer.

22
00:01:12.500 --> 00:01:13.433
Rise.

23
00:01:15.533 --> 00:01:16.966
I summoned you to the palace.

24
00:01:16.966 --> 00:01:18.433
I made you a Noble Consort

25
00:01:18.600 --> 00:01:20.966
because I find you clever and considerate.

26
00:01:21.133 --> 00:01:23.633
I also know you have been with the Emperor for a long time.

27
00:01:24.166 --> 00:01:26.166
But you saw just now

28
00:01:26.166 --> 00:01:28.266
how much the Emperor favors Su Qingyun.

29
00:01:29.500 --> 00:01:31.266
I understand the Empress Dowager’s intention.

30
00:01:31.566 --> 00:01:34.700
You’re afraid that Noble Consort Rong will become too powerful in the harem.

31
00:01:34.700 --> 00:01:36.600
Be smart in the future.

32
00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:38.100
Just follow Su Qingyun

33
00:01:38.100 --> 00:01:40.666
and serve the Emperor by his side.

34
00:01:40.666 --> 00:01:42.366
Don’t worry about other matters.

35
00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:44.966
Based on my understanding of the Emperor,

36
00:01:44.966 --> 00:01:47.566
the harem cannot temporarily belong to the Song family.

37
00:01:47.566 --> 00:01:49.766
Otherwise, it would implicate the Song family.

38
00:01:49.866 --> 00:01:51.400
I won’t be able to protect you.

39
00:01:51.400 --> 00:01:53.100
I will heed your advice, Your Highness.

40
00:01:53.266 --> 00:01:56.566
If there is anything I do not understand, I will come to ask you.

41
00:01:57.066 --> 00:02:01.366
Let Wang Mo Mo assist in the Yao Hua Palace now.
